data.description: Terrific recent construction on a quiet, cul-de-sac street in the heart of Spring Branch. Beautiful open living spaces with high ceilings, top-of-the-line finishes, designer colors and a terrific backyard will wow any buyer. The first floor, with travertine flooring throughout, is perfect for entertaining with the fabulous kitchen opening to the living and dining rooms. The amazing island kitchen is adorned with Viking appliances, a dry bar, appliance garage and site-built cabinetry. There is a wonderful study at the back of the house. Travel upstairs to find hardwoods throughout, a game room, master suite and 3 additional bedrooms. The master suite includes a sitting area, balcony a gorgeous bath with double sinks, large vanity area, free standing tub, spacious shower and walk-in closets. All secondary bedrooms are spacious and have a tremendous amount of natural light. The backyard is perfect with a covered patio and enough grassy area for a small pool.
